Class CellObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • physicalLayer.CellObject
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Resource, Stone, Trap, Water

    public abstract class CellObject
extends java.lang.Object
    An abstract class to model an object that is contained in a Cell. Objects reside in one cell only.
    Version:
    v1.2
    Author:
    Chloe M. Barnes
